-align: -0.838ex; width:1.262ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \ga=
mma }"></span> at the intersection of the diagonals:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-9" =
class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parallelogram#=
cite_note-9"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>9<span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
